<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 15:15:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>信中显示，民主党议员就华为产品中的台积电芯片问题向拜登发起攻击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-lawmaker-takes-aim-biden-over-tsmc-chip-huawei-product-document-shows-2024-10-31/</link><description>民主党参议员马克·沃纳 (Mark Warner) 批评拜登政府对台积电的“监控明显松懈”，此前有报道称，这家台湾芯片制造商生产的芯片最终被用于中国受到严厉制裁的华为生产的产品中。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 13:24:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/democratic-lawmaker-takes-aim-biden-over-tsmc-chip-huawei-product-document-shows-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>政府支持的媒体称，中国工商总局否认与欧盟就电动汽车进行谈判的报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-denies-reports-negotiations-with-eu-evs-govt-backed-media-says-2024-10-31/</link><description>据当地政府支持的《上海观察家报》周四报道，中国上汽集团被欧盟征收最高的电动汽车附加关税（35.3%），该公司驳斥了有关与欧盟就此事单独谈判的报道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 11:41:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-denies-reports-negotiations-with-eu-evs-govt-backed-media-says-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>越南敦促中国释放在南海被扣押的渔民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-china-release-detained-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-31/</link><description>外交部发言人周四表示，越南对中国在南海有争议的西沙群岛扣留越南渔民和渔船的行为提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 10:39:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-urges-china-release-detained-fishermen-south-china-sea-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>官员称印尼将对南海事件做出适当反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-respond-appropriately-south-china-sea-incidents-official-says-2024-10-31/</link><description>周四，在一艘中国海警船中断雅加达国有能源公司的调查后，印尼在南海问题上的立场保持不变，并将采取适当行动以保护其领土。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 07:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/indonesia-respond-appropriately-south-china-sea-incidents-official-says-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>台风“康瑞”袭来，上海迎来暴雨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/chinas-shanghai-braces-torrential-rain-typhoon-kong-rey-advances-2024-10-31/</link><description>中国金融中心上海正面临40多年来最严重的降雨，台风“康瑞”预计将从南部登陆，并在未来两天席卷东部沿海。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 05:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/chinas-shanghai-braces-torrential-rain-typhoon-kong-rey-advances-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>据Politico报道，美国通过与中国公民的交易确保牧师从中国获释</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-secured-release-pastor-china-with-trade-chinese-citizen-politico-reports-2024-10-31/</link><description>据《Politico》周三援引三名知情人士的话报道，美国上个月以一名中国公民为条件，从中国释放了美国牧师林大卫 (David Lin)。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 02:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-secured-release-pastor-china-with-trade-chinese-citizen-politico-reports-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国10月非制造业活动恢复扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-non-manufacturing-activity-breaks-back-into-expansion-2024-10-31/</link><description>周四的一项官方调查显示，中国十月份非制造业活动有所扩张，这让政策制定者松了一口气，尽管其他指标表明世界第二大经济体的复苏仍然遥远。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:47:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-oct-non-manufacturing-activity-breaks-back-into-expansion-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国制造业活动六个月来首次扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-oct-manufacturing-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-10-31/</link><description>十月份服务业也有所回升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:38:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-oct-manufacturing-activity-expands-first-time-six-months-2024-10-31/</guid></item><item><title>雷诺老板表示，欧盟根据世贸组织规则对中国电动汽车征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-electric-cars-based-wto-rules-renault-boss-says-2024-10-30/</link><description>法国汽车制造商雷诺首席执行官卢卡·德·梅奥表示，欧盟周三对中国进口电动汽车征收的关税是基于世界贸易组织制定的规则，每个人都签署了这些规则。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:55:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-tariffs-chinese-electric-cars-based-wto-rules-renault-boss-says-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国要求汽车制造商暂停对支持电动汽车关税的欧盟国家的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-tells-carmakers-pause-investment-eu-countries-backing-ev-tariffs-sources-2024-10-30/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国已要求其汽车制造商停止对支持对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税的欧洲国家进行大规模投资，此举可能会进一步分裂欧洲。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:09:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-tells-carmakers-pause-investment-eu-countries-backing-ev-tariffs-sources-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>印度官员称，印度和中国已完成从边境对峙点撤军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-complete-troops-pull-back-border-face-off-points-indian-defence-2024-10-30/</link><description>印度国防官员周三表示，印度和中国已按计划从有争议的喜马拉雅边境的两个对峙点撤军。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 11:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/india-china-complete-troops-pull-back-border-face-off-points-indian-defence-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>前央行顾问表示，中国的刺激措施应与改革齐头并进</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stimulus-should-go-hand-hand-with-reforms-ex-cbank-adviser-says-2024-10-30/</link><description>前央行顾问刘世锦在周三发表的讲话中表示，中国的刺激措施可能会付出代价，必须与改革同时进行，以确保经济可持续增长。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 09:17:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stimulus-should-go-hand-hand-with-reforms-ex-cbank-adviser-says-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国工商总局将提起诉讼反对欧盟对电动汽车的裁决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-file-lawsuit-countering-eus-ruling-evs-2024-10-30/</link><description>中国上汽集团表示，在欧盟裁定将中国制造的电动汽车关税提高至高达45.3%后，上汽集团拟向欧盟法院提起诉讼，以保护自身权益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 08:31:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-saic-file-lawsuit-countering-eus-ruling-evs-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国即将推出的财政刺激方案将稳定而非提振经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-looming-fiscal-package-set-stabilise-rather-than-boost-growth-2024-10-30/</link><description>正在制定的措施代表了一种更加精准的刺激方法，这与之前全面重振增长的战略背道而驰。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 07:11:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-looming-fiscal-package-set-stabilise-rather-than-boost-growth-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>中国在被问及特朗普言论时称台湾可能会被“抛弃”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-implies-trump-could-discard-taiwan-2024-10-30/</link><description>中国周三暗示，如果美国共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普赢得11月5日大选，他可以“抛弃”台湾，称美国一贯奉行“美国优先”政策。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:56:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-implies-trump-could-discard-taiwan-2024-10-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>